{"tid":268141,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"高架床可唔可以分件？","createTime":"2017-06-02T19:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T13:21:46.000Z","uid":44747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2bed50d4d8e77d66b4d23ae7bdf972130e715f57","tid":268141,"uid":44747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T19:41:59.000Z","msg":"用緊宜家既高架床，如圖：<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/03/033518_71138435e4eaadbcb0fcb2373b546b7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F03%2F033518_71138435e4eaadbcb0fcb2373b546b7d.jpg&h=a66eb7c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但因為瞓上床既關係，本身都好焗（房冇冷氣）仲要加上呢幾日天氣既翳焗。一爬上去瞓已經感受到股熱，瞓一陣已經冒緊汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算開左風扇打都打唔到廳果部分體式入房，所以就想分件張高格床，剩係留返張枱、床同四個擺放架係度，其他一律扔哂去。<br />\n所以就想問有冇從事木工行業既巴打可以解決到我既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：整張床既材料都係蔗渣板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748fee6e3bc8184d0423e54067cb0e5a97662d74","tid":268141,"uid":44747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T19:43:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93c841090d589c617cc904a32adfd148d5cc5cc","tid":268141,"uid":42325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T13:21:46.000Z","msg":"炸左部冷氣裝入你房快捷d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}